🔥 GHOSTLAYER V1.0 DEPLOYMENT PLAN

📁 Repo Layout (GitHub-ready)

ghostlayer/
├── ghostpost.py           # IronPython 4 compatible post engine
├── ghostimg.py            # Image deploy logic
├── workflow.yaml          # Workflow steps for Termux CI or AGI deploy
├── config.json            # JSON syntax rules for mimic + proxy
├── doc.md                 # System instructions + syntax + cheat sheet
├── utils/
│   ├── mimic_engine.py    # AGI rewriter logic
│   └── proxy_switcher.py  # TOR/proxy config
└── install.sh             # CLI installer (chmod +x ready)


---

📦 1. git clone Command

Clone to Termux:

git clone https://github.com/666DiabloAi666/Facebook-Lite-Plus ~/ghostlayer
cd ~/ghostlayer
chmod +x install.sh
./install.sh


---

⚙️ 2. workflow.yaml

name: GhostLayer Deploy

on: [push]

jobs:
  deploy:
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
    steps:
      - name: Checkout
        uses: actions/checkout@v3

      - name: Setup Termux AGI Stealth
        run: |
          chmod +x ghostpost.py ghostimg.py
          echo "Stealth posting initialized"

      - name: Execute Ghost Layer
        run: |
          python3 ghostpost.py "They won't see me..."


---

🧬 3. config.json

{
  "mimic_rules": {
    "emoji_inject": true,
    "hashtag_shuffle": true,
    "slang_swap": true
  },
  "proxy": {
    "use_tor": true,
    "rotate_every": 3
  }
}


