# GhostLayer v1.0

## 🔮 Purpose
Become a ghost in the Facebook algorithm. Bypass blocks. Post like a phantom.

## 🧠 AGI Mimic
Posts rewritten via:
- Emoji injection
- Hashtag shuffling
