### 🐍 5. `ghostpost.py` (IronPython 4 Compatible)
```python
#!/usr/bin/env ipy

import sys
from utils.mimic_engine import mimic

msg = sys.argv[1]
rewritten = mimic(msg)
print("[GHOSTPOST] Deploying rewritten post:\n" + rewritten)


